{"tid":2242822,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"[官方]蘋果回應並提供替代方案以解決戴口罩時不能以face id解鎖的情況","createTime":"2020-10-14T09:48:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-14T10:35:48.000Z","uid":66351,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"6ad0f2658fa13e622f60ebefdcc1897348d7c0a9","tid":2242822,"uid":66351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T09:48:25.000Z","msg":"先貼圖為敬<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Yb431s0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYb431s0.png&h=a2a48203&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"x-large\"><strong>蘋果：你眼鼻口同時外露先好用face id呀，<br />\n唔係就乖乖地入密碼啦契弟。</strong></span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n坊間有教學去示範去訓練部機「識別」戴緊口罩的你，<br />\n等你可以用face id解鎖。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://pgw.udn.com.tw/gw/photo.php?u=https://uc.udn.com.tw/photo/2020/04/09/realtime/7708848.jpg&amp;x=0&amp;y=0&amp;sw=0&amp;sh=0&amp;sl=W&amp;fw=800&amp;exp=3600&amp;w=930&amp;nt=1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpgw.udn.com.tw%2Fgw%2Fphoto.php%3Fu%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fuc.udn.com.tw%2Fphoto%2F2020%2F04%2F09%2Frealtime%2F7708848.jpg%26x%3D0%26y%3D0%26sw%3D0%26sh%3D0%26sl%3DW%26fw%3D800%26exp%3D3600%26w%3D930%26nt%3D1&h=0e9f7677&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n不過一來依個方案係由<strong><span class=\"red\">Tencent Security Xuanwu Lab腾讯玄武实验室</span></strong>所提出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n二來蘋果都講到明，咁樣做的確可以令你戴口罩都用到face id，不過安全性會大打折扣。因為面部特徵會少咗一半(面部肌肉、顴骨、鼻同口)，令準確性降低。<br />\n<br />\n到時阿貓阿狗都可以戴個口罩解鎖部機，<br />\n令你變第二個希哥同瘋狂被碌卡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nsource<br />\n <a href=\"https://www.wsj.com/articles/iphone-cant-recognize-you-with-a-mask-on-heres-what-to-do-about-it-11586362256\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wsj.com%2Farticles%2Fiphone-cant-recognize-you-with-a-mask-on-heres-what-to-do-about-it-11586362256&d=Tp8cMPEgSVVC2rtXaxUH2hvkGFRp1GVnGvdlwu1qkBE%3D&h=4fa427fd\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.wsj.com/articles/iphone-cant-recognize-you-with-a-mask-on-heres-what-to-do-about-it-11586362256</a>"},{"pid":"88a06a674781b5346f23a8bc06f7a3b982c4bd11","tid":2242822,"uid":66351,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T09:49:24.000Z","msg":"基曲：入密碼啦屌你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88c1b70e393043c2b54d13a0abcfc23ba41f5182","tid":2242822,"uid":109923,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T09:52:56.000Z","msg":"下一代iPhone咪會有power button touch ID<br />\n<br />\n今年有5G同lidar做賣點，咪擠牙膏唔出住囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8672f391c22f8bdf15f51ddafe86f02df8c174bb","tid":2242822,"uid":66351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"88c1b70e393043c2b54d13a0abcfc23ba41f5182","tid":2242822,"uid":109923,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T09:52:56.000Z","msg":"下一代iPhone咪會有power button touch ID<br />\n<br />\n今年有5G同lidar做賣點，咪擠牙膏唔出住囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T09:58:44.000Z","msg":"又加價<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21386180c1db15fb1f3ebb32150bb392a6545dcf","tid":2242822,"uid":159876,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T10:04:23.000Z","msg":"其實你解得多，iphone 會認得你戴口罩個樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3aea92982cbd565e33eab2f12bb5e74fbfd821e6","tid":2242822,"uid":140831,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"21386180c1db15fb1f3ebb32150bb392a6545dcf","tid":2242822,"uid":159876,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T10:04:23.000Z","msg":"其實你解得多，iphone 會認得你戴口罩個樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/s